IndiVision Clothing Dataset

1. Purpose and Origin
This dataset has been assembled exclusively for non-commercial educational and research purposes as part of the Deep Learning for Computer Vision (CSE3292) curriculum. 
The images in this dataset were collected from various publicly accessible internet sources, including e-commerce platforms, government handloom portals, and educational institutions.

