The creators of this dataset make no claim of copyright ownership over the individual images contained herein.
The compilation and distribution of this dataset are conducted under the principles of "Fair Use" (or equivalent educational exceptions to copyright) for the purpose of academic research, teaching, scholarship, and algorithmic testing.
All original copyrights remain with their respective owners. Sources for individual images are documented where possible in the metadata.

